WEBVTT

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:31.976
Kerabai had a valid question,

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:33.456
so in this drought,

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:37.080
we decided to start
the cattle camp in the area.

00:08:37.400 --> 00:08:41.736
It's where farmers can bring
their animals to one place

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:44.159
and get fodder and water.

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:46.856
It didn't rain.

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:49.736
Cattle camp was extended for 18 months.

00:08:49.760 --> 00:08:53.056
Kerabai used to move around
in the cattle camp

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:56.216
and sing the songs of encouragement.

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:57.960
Kerabai became very popular.

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:02.616
It rained and cattle camp was ended,